</ul>
<p>(7)施密特正交化</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="C:%5CUsers%5C%E5%AD%9F%E4%B9%90%E8%88%AA%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20220516202346423.png" alt="image-20220516202346423" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>(8)矩阵的幂</p>
<p>​	A<sup>m</sup>=AAAAAA···AAA（共m个）称为A的m次幂</p>
<p>(9)方阵乘积的行列式 |<strong>AB</strong>|=|<strong>A</strong>||<strong>B</strong>|</p>
